Dialogue: 9,0:00:21.91,0:00:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não acho que ninguém tenha tentado filtrar o lubrificante.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:25.79,0:00:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos lá.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:34.26,0:00:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:35.55,0:00:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Você conseguiu, Tanikaze{**-kun}!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:37.39,0:00:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Água! Temos água, Hoshijiro!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:44.77,0:00:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossível!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:51.82,0:00:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,São esses os Garde?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:54.70,0:00:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uau.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:55.99,0:00:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,256 quadros em propulsão reversa.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:58.78,0:01:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles vieram atrás de nós!
Dialogue: 9,0:01:02.91,0:01:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Viva!
Dialogue: 9,0:01:03.79,0:01:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nós vamos sobreviver!
