Dialogue: 9,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, espera!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:59.97,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0.]
Dialogue: 9,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A culpa é sua, Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:36.08,0:20:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Você consegue andar?! Impossível.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos voltar para dentro.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:51.14,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Minha culpa?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:53.19,0:20:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que as Honokas disseram isso?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,E os Gauna, Izana?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Como eu cheguei aqui?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Apenas se acalme.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:04.61,0:21:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Izana...]
Dialogue: 9,0:21:06.62,0:21:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:08.12,0:21:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Você não parece bem.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Você deveria dormir, Nagate.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu estou bem.
