Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:48.38,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Até que meus instintos vacilarem
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:48.38,ED1-Rom,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Até que a honra se apague
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:50.64,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Até que minha chama se apague
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:50.64,ED1-Rom,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Até que o fogo se extinga
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:52.93,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Meus impulsos persistirão
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:52.93,ED1-Rom,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Sem cessar o confronto
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:55.10,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Nossa formação voará
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:55.10,ED1-Rom,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Shoui... para este céu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:59.81,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Uma estrela silenciosa{Hoshijiro Shizuka} vagueia
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:59.81,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,[T0[T1]Hoshijiro Shizuka]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:59.81,ED1-Rom,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Uma estrela calma vaga por aí
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:02.40,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}De encruzilhada em encruzilhada{Kunato}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:02.40,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,[T0[T1]Kunato]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:02.40,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,[T0[T1]Kunato]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:02.40,ED1-Rom,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}O tempo de Kunato
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.11,0:23:04.23,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}na escuridão sem fim
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.11,0:23:04.23,ED1-Rom,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}na escuridão sem saída
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:06.69,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}seu coração é meu lar?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:06.69,ED1-Rom,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}será no seu peito que eu volto?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.69,0:23:09.03,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}são os confins do universo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.69,0:23:09.03,ED1-Rom,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}ou no limite do céu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:13.78,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}por qual caminho minha dor me guiará?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:13.78,ED1-Rom,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}até onde esta dor me levará?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:22.88,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Eu sou feito de grãos de emoção
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:22.88,ED1-Rom,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Partículas de emoção que me permeiam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:30.68,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Que fazem fotossíntese da sua luz
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:30.68,ED1-Rom,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Fotossíntese buscando você
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:35.56,ED1-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Um fogo fraco{Honoka}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:35.56,ED1-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\pos(657,644)}{\blur5\alpha&H88&\b1\fsp2\fs-4\c&HFFE15F&}Suave
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:35.56,ED1-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Uma luz suave
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:40.35,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}Desenha-os em um longo caminho
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:40.35,ED1-Rom,,80,420,0,,[T0[T1]nagaki michi izanau]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:44.86,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}para o futuro que protegemos{Gardes}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:44.86,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)\pos(654,645)}{\blur5\alpha&H88&\b1\fsp2\fs-4\c&HFFE15F&}Garde
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:44.86,ED1-Rom,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}para o amanhã que deve ser protegido
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:52.36,ED1-Eng,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}E mesmo que meu corpo seja dilacerado,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:52.36,ED1-Rom,,80,420,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}mesmo que este corpo se desfaça, manterei o espírito de luta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.78,0:23:54.53,ED1-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur5}o futuro ainda sentirá nosso espírito de combate{Tsugumori}
